== 应用 ==
=== 生物学应用 ===
2-巯基乙醇可以打开[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]中存在的[[二硫键|二硫键]]：
:[[胱氨酸|cysS-Scys]]  +  2 HOCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>SH   →   2 [[半胱氨酸|cysSH]]  +  HOCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>S-SCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>OH

:[[File:Disulfide-bond-cleavage-by-2-mercaptoethanol-2D-skeletal.svg|400px]]

二硫键被打开后可以使蛋白质的[[四级结构|四级]]或[[三级结构|三级结构]]被破坏。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.chemicalland21.com/specialtychem/finechem/2-MERCAPTOETHANOL.htm | publisher = Chemicalland21.com | title = 2-Mercaptoethanol | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061005223640/http://www.chemicalland21.com/specialtychem/finechem/2-MERCAPTOETHANOL.htm | archivedate = 2006-10-05 | accessdate = 2008-06-12 }}</ref>由于2-巯基乙醇能够打开蛋白质的结构，它常常被用于蛋白质分析。而2-巯基乙醇也常常被用于保护蛋白质中自由的[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]][[巯基|巯基]]之间不会错误形成二硫键。

作为还原剂，2-巯基乙醇常常可以与[[二硫苏糖醇|二硫苏糖醇]]（DTT）或[[三(2-甲酰乙基)膦盐酸盐|三(2-甲酰乙基)膦盐酸盐]]（TCEP）互换使用。

2-巯基乙醇是少数几种被发现可以延长小鼠寿命的化合物。<ref>{{cite journal | author = M.L. Heidrick, L.C. Hendricks and D.E. Cook | journal = [[Mech._Ageing_Dev.|Mech. Ageing Dev.]] | title = Effect of dietary 2-mercaptoethanol on the life span, immune system, tumor incidence and lipid peroxidation damage in spleen lymphocytes of aging BC3F1 mice | volume = 27 | year = 1984 | issue = 3 | pages = 341-58 | pmid = 6334792 | doi = 10.1016/0047-6374(84)90057-5}}</ref>在[[微克|微克]]量级水平上，2-巯基乙醇被观察到对实验鼠的生命具有多种可能的正面效应。<ref>{{cite journal | author = L. Pénzesa, R. C. Nobleb, E. Beregia, S. Imrec, J. Izsáka and O. Regius | title = Effect of 2-mercaptoethanol on some metabolic indices of ageing of CBA/Ca inbred mice | journal = [[Mech._Ageing_Dev.|Mech. Ageing Dev.]] | volume = 45 | issue = 1 | pages = 75-92 | year = 1988 | doi = 10.1016/0047-6374(88)90021-8 | pmid = 3216730}}</ref>

=== 其他 ===
2-巯基乙醇可以与[[醛|醛]]或[[酮|酮]]反应，生成相应的氧硫杂环化合物，这使得2-巯基乙醇可以作为[[羰基|羰基]]的[[保护基|保护基]]：<ref>{{cite web | title = 1,3-Dithiolanes, 1,3-Dithianes | url = https://www.organic-chemistry.org/protectivegroups/carbonyl/1,3-dithiolanes.htm | publisher = Organic Chemistry Portal | accessdate = 2018-08-05 | archive-date = 2008-05-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517162047/http://www.organic-chemistry.org/protectivegroups/carbonyl/1,3-dithiolanes.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

